title: Plenty for fans to experience at English Field as Virginia Tech Baseball concludes regular season - VT hokiesports.com
content: Plenty for fans to experience at English Field as Virginia Tech Baseball concludes regular season  VT hokiesports.com
description: The Virginia Tech baseball team is arguably the hottest squad in the country, having won 24 of its last 28 games and ascending to a No. 5 national ranking heading into the final weeks of regular season play.
